      <title>国会希望微软的史密斯就安全漏洞作证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/congress-wants-microsoft-s-smith-to-testify-on-security-lapses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院委员会已邀请微软公司总裁布拉德·史密斯 (Brad Smith) 就该公司如何应对美国政府官员的微软电子邮件账户遭到黑客攻击以及其他违规行为作出证词。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/congress-wants-microsoft-s-smith-to-testify-on-security-lapses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 13:11:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称俄罗斯正试图在哈尔科夫附近发动新的攻势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/zelenskiy-says-russia-attempts-new-offensive-near-kharkiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，随着克里姆林宫军队突破东北部边境，俄罗斯对乌克兰第二大城市周围的领土发动了新的攻势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/zelenskiy-says-russia-attempts-new-offensive-near-kharkiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 12:47:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利在习近平访问期间深化与华为的关系，规避风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hungary-deepens-huawei-ties-during-xi-visit-shunning-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在习近平主席本周访问布达佩斯期间，匈牙利同意深化与中国电信设备制造商华为技术有限公司的关系，此举可能会进一步加剧该国与西方盟友的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hungary-deepens-huawei-ties-during-xi-visit-shunning-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 11:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安暂停公共支出热潮以应对通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/erdogan-s-public-spending-craze-to-pause-over-turkey-inflation-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 赖以政治生涯的公共支出狂潮即将降温，因为政府准备冻结新项目以专注于对抗通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/erdogan-s-public-spending-craze-to-pause-over-turkey-inflation-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 11:03:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊斯兰国在莫桑比克发动三年来最大胆的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/islamic-state-stages-boldest-attack-in-mozambique-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，与伊斯兰国有关的叛乱分子袭击了莫桑比克富含天然气的德尔加杜角省的马科米亚镇，这是他们三年多来最大胆的袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/islamic-state-stages-boldest-attack-in-mozambique-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非可能因天然气泵退出而限制壳牌石油勘探</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/south-africa-may-curb-shell-s-oil-exploration-over-gas-pump-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非能源部表示，由于壳牌公司计划退出南非燃料供应业务，南非能源部可能会减少向该公司发放的石油勘探许可证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/south-africa-may-curb-shell-s-oil-exploration-over-gas-pump-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:52:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登对中国加征关税的计划主要是象征性的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/biden-s-plan-to-hit-china-with-more-tariffs-is-mostly-symbolic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登将对中国经济复苏的核心行业征收关税，这似乎是对其国家最大竞争对手的大胆打击。事实上，这些限制措施几乎不会削弱北京的经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/biden-s-plan-to-hit-china-with-more-tariffs-is-mostly-symbolic</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度反对党领袖因竞选活动被释放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/indian-opposition-leader-gets-interim-bail-for-national-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院已批准德里首席部长阿尔温德·凯杰里瓦尔临时保释，直至正在进行的选举结束，从而允许反对派联盟的主要领导人开展反对总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党的竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/indian-opposition-leader-gets-interim-bail-for-national-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 09:07:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京要求议员重新任命俄罗斯总理米舒斯京</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/putin-asks-lawmakers-to-reappoint-mishustin-as-russian-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗拉基米尔·普京总统要求俄罗斯议会重新任命米哈伊尔·米舒斯京为总理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/putin-asks-lawmakers-to-reappoint-mishustin-as-russian-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 03:44:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将通过关税打击中国电动汽车等战略行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/biden-poised-to-impose-tariffs-on-china-evs-strategic-sectors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，美国总统拜登的政府准备最早于下周公布对中国商品关税的全面决定，预计该决定将针对关键战略领域征收新税，同时拒绝唐纳德·特朗普寻求的全面加税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/biden-poised-to-impose-tariffs-on-china-evs-strategic-sectors</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 00:45:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
